Monitoring scripts from https://github.com/kubernetes/heapster/blob/master/docs/influxdb.md

Initial setup
The default user name and password is 'admin'.
Once you login to Grafana, add a datasource that is InfluxDB.
InfluxDB version 0.8.x.
The URL for InfluxDB will be http://:8086. Database name is 'k8s'. Default user name and password is 'root'.
